                    </Text>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: How do I check flight status?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: You can check your flight status in the 'My Bookings' section or by searching for flights in the 'Search Flights' section. Flight status updates include on-time, delayed, or cancelled information." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: What's included in the ticket price?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: The base ticket price includes your seat, carry-on baggage, and basic in-flight service. Additional services like meals, extra baggage, and seat selection may be available for an additional fee." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: What are the different class options?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: We offer Economy, Business, and First Class options. Economy provides comfortable seating and basic amenities, Business Class offers enhanced comfort and premium services, while First Class provides luxury amenities and personalized service." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: How early should I arrive at the airport?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: For domestic flights, arrive at least 2 hours before departure. For international flights, arrive at least 3 hours before departure to allow time for check-in, security screening, and any additional procedures." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                </VBox>
                
                <!-- Payment FAQs -->
                <VBox fx:id="paymentSection" spacing="15" styleClass="content-card">
                    <padding>
                        <Insets bottom="20.0" left="20.0" right="20.0" top="20.0" />
