                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: How can I contact customer support?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: You can contact support by submitting a ticket through the 'Support Tickets' section on your dashboard, using our AI Assistant for immediate help, or viewing your submitted tickets in 'View My Tickets'." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: What information should I include in a support ticket?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Include your booking reference number, a clear description of your issue, any relevant dates, and your contact information. The more details you provide, the faster we can assist you." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: How quickly will I receive a response to my support ticket?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: We aim to respond to all support tickets within 24 hours. Urgent matters are prioritized and may receive faster responses. You can track the status of your tickets in the 'View My Tickets' section." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: What can the AI Assistant help me with?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Our AI Assistant can help with booking information, flight status queries, general questions about policies, and guide you through common procedures. For complex issues, it can direct you to submit a support ticket." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                </VBox>
                
                <!-- Account FAQs -->
