                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Click on the 'Profile' button in the top right corner of your dashboard to access your account settings. You can update your personal information, contact details, and preferences from there." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: How do I change my password?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Go to your Profile settings and look for the password change option. You'll need to enter your current password and choose a new secure password. Make sure to use a strong password with a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: What if I forget my login credentials?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Use the 'Forgot Password' link on the login page to reset your password. If you've forgotten your username, contact customer support with your account details for assistance." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                    
                    <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="faq-item">
                        <Text text="Q: Can I delete my account?" styleClass="faq-question">
                            <font><Font name="System Bold" size="16" /></font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text text="A: Yes, you can request account deletion by contacting customer support. Please note that this action is permanent and will remove all your booking history and account data." styleClass="faq-answer" />
                    </VBox>
                </VBox>
                
                <!-- Still Need Help Section -->
